##### MF4: ANGULAR DISTRIBUTIONS OF SECONDARY PARTICLES           4228 1451
                                                                  4228 1451
We use MF4 for the neutron scattering angular distribution for    4228 1451
discrete levels.                                                  4228 1451
                                                                  4228 1451
- MT2      : Elastic angular distribution                         4228 1451
                                                                  4228 1451
The flag LTT=3 is used to indicate a switch at some high energy,  4228 1451
generally 50 MeV, from a Legendre representation to a tabulated   4228 1451
representation. For incident energies below this energy, the      4228 1451
Legendre coefficients are given on a sufficiently precise energy  4228 1451
grid. They are a sum of calculated Legendre coefficients for      4228 1451
compound nucleus and shape-elastic scattering. For higher         4228 1451
incident energies, relative angular distributions are tabulated   4228 1451
on an angular grid.                                               4228 1451
                                                                  4228 1451
- MT51-70  : (n,n') angular distribution for 1st-20th state       4228 1451
- MT600-610: (n,p) angular distribution for 0th-10th state        4228 1451
